OL,3,CMan admits stalking Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing judge Shirley Ballas
OL,6,FStrictly Come Dancing judge Shirley
OL,7,FBallas moved her mother to a different
OL,8,Fhome and increased security measures
OL,9,Fdue to a stalker, a court has heard.
OL,11,FKyle Shaw, 37, pleaded guilty at
OL,12,FLiverpool Crown Court to stalking
OL,13,FBallas, 64, causing serious harm or
OL,14,Fdistress, between August 31 2017 and
OL,15,FNovember 29 2023.
