OL,3,CMan admits stalking Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing judge Shirley Ballas
OL,6,FThe court heard he made continued
OL,7,Funwanted attempts to contact Ballas,
OL,8,Fposted on social media about the star,
OL,9,Fincluding posting an image of her
OL,10,Fhouse on social media, attempted to
OL,11,Fcontact her family, friends and work
OL,12,Fcolleagues, monitored her online and
OL,13,FTV presence and made arrangements to
OL,14,Fattend her book tour.
