OL,3,CMan admits stalking Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing judge Shirley Ballas
OL,6,FAccording to the charge, his actions
OL,7,Fhad a "substantial adverse effect" on
OL,8,FBallas's usual day-to-day activities
OL,9,Fas she increased her security
OL,10,Fmeasures, relocated her mother to a
OL,11,Fdifferent property and made different
OL,12,Farrangements surrounding her social
OL,13,Fand work arrangements.
OL,15,FShaw also admitted possession of
OL,16,Fcannabis. The defendant, of Whetstone
OL,17,FLane in Birkenhead, Wirral, was given
OL,18,Fconditional bail ahead of a sentencing
OL,19,Fhearing due to take place on April 1.
